result.formatted_address: Hong Kong, Repulse Bay, 泳灘道33號
result.name: Pizza Hut

reviews.text:
Pizza Hut is not as bad as you think. Try the Super Supreme and Hawaiian. They are my favorite pizza flavors. It is very good when served hot or delivered hot not, to mention it is very affordable. Take note, always order Large Size for 1-2 pax. 🤗

Just had a delivery yesterday and just like the times before that, I had a very good experience. The pizza was served hot and delicious. Plus points for delivering even when it was raining, that's when we need the delivery services the most.
Food is so far so good. The price is reasonable comparing to other restaurants. Facing beach but many coaches block the sea view.
It was delicious 🍕 with thin tasty substrate😋

what a joke - rude service, poor quality of food.
unreal for a chain place like this.

Hey guys, if you have money to loose and want to eat the worst pizza the earth is never known do yourself a favor. You will pay acual bread with some plastic on it and if you are lucky, you will get some expired food with an inexistant service and sometimes also rude. Please DO NOT EAT HERE for your safety and your wallet. If you want to eat an actual good pizza, you should go to pizza express, maybe 50$ more but with  an infinite difference in quality.
